eq\pm\mathrm{id}\), 则存在\(\mathscr{B}\in M\), s.t. \(\mathscr{AB=-BA}\) 证明: \(M\)中的元素个数不超过\(2n^{2}\). 证明: (提示: 证明一个集合元素个数不超过线性空间的维数, 可以去证明这个集合的元素是线性无关的. 此处\(n^{2}\)暗示维数, \(\mathscr{A},-\mathscr{A}\)可以同时出现, 所以有个 2 倍.) 首先证明\( orall\mathscr{A}\in M\), 都有\(\mathscr{A}^{2}=\pm\mathrm{id}\). 任取\(\mathscr{A}\in M\) , 由(2)得\(\mathscr{A}^{2}\in M\). 如果\(\mathscr{A}^{2}
eq\pm\mathrm{id}\) , 则由(4), \(\exists\mathscr{B}\in M\), s.t. \(\mathscr{A}^{2}\mathscr{B}=-\mathscr{BA}^{2}\). 另一方面, 若\(\mathscr{AB}=\mathscr{BA}\), 则\(\mathscr{A}^{2}\mathscr{B}=\mathscr{A}(\mathscr{AB})=\mathscr{A}(\mathscr{BA})=(\mathscr{AB})\mathscr{A}=\mathscr{B}\mathscr{A}^{2}\); 若\(\mathscr{AB}=-\mathscr{BA}\), 则\(\mathscr{A}^{2}\mathscr{B}=\mathscr{A}(\mathscr{AB})=\mathscr{A}(-\mathscr{BA})=-(\mathscr{AB})\mathscr{A}=\mathscr{B}\mathscr{A}^{2}\). 即总有\(\mathscr{A}^{2}\mathscr{B}=\mathscr{B}\mathscr{A}^{2}\). 所以\(M
i\mathscr{A}^{2}\mathscr{B}=0\), 这与(1)矛盾. 然后证明\(M\)中不同且不互为相反数的元素线性无关. (反证法)假设\(M\)中不同且不互为相反数的元素线性相关, 那么一定可以找到一个最小的\(n\), 使得\(M\)中不同且不互为相反数的\(n\)个元素线性相关. 设\(\mathscr{A}_{1}, \mathscr{A}_{2}, \cdots, \mathscr{A}_{n}\in M\)互不相同且\( orall i
