eq\pm\mathrm{id}\)和(4)可知\(\mathscr{C}\in M\), s.t. \(\mathscr{A}_{n}\mathscr{C}=-\mathscr{C}\mathscr{A}_{n}\). 不妨假设对\(1\leq i\leq t\), \(\mathscr{A}_{i}\mathscr{C}=\mathscr{C}\mathscr{A}_{i}\); 对\(t+1\leq i\leq n-1\), \(\mathscr{A}_{i}\mathscr{C}=-\mathscr{C}\mathscr{A}_{i}\). 对式子 \[ \sum_{i=1}^{n-1}k_{i}\mathscr{A}_{i}=-k_{n}\mathscr{A}_{n} \] 分别用\(\mathscr{C}\)左作用和右作用, 得 \[ \sum_{i=1}^{t}k_{i}\mathscr{C}\mathscr{A}_{i}+\sum_{i=t}^{n-1}k_{i}\mathscr{C}\mathscr{A}_{i}=-k_{n}\mathscr{C}\mathscr{A}_{n} \] \[ \sum_{i=1}^{t}k_{i}\mathscr{A}_{i}\mathscr{C}+\sum_{i=t}^{n-1}k_{i}\mathscr{A}_{i}\mathscr{C}=-k_{n}\mathscr{A}_{n}\mathscr{C} \] 由于对\(t+1\leq i\leq n\), \(\mathscr{A}_{i}\mathscr{C}=-\mathscr{C}\mathscr{A}_{i}\). 故将两式相加, 得到 \[ \sum_{i=1}^{t}k_{i}\mathscr{C}\mathscr{A}_{i}=0 \] 而\(t\leq n-1\), 与\(n\)的最小性矛盾. 因此, \(M\)中不同且不互为相反数的元素线性无关. 而\(\dim M\leq n^{2}\). 故\(\left|Might|\leq2n^{2}\). \(\square\) 问题 2 [Dedekind-Artin] 设\(G\)是一个幺半群, \(\mathbb{K}\)是一个域 (则\(K^{*} := \mathbb{K}-\{0\}\)是一个群). \(\sigma_{1},\sigma_{2},\ldots,\sigma_{n}\)是两两不同的非零同态\(Gightarrow K^{*}\), 则它们在\(\mathbb{K}\)上线性无关. 证明: 假设存在这样的一组非零同态, 使得它们在\(\mathbb{K}\)上线性无关, 则一定能找到其中元素个数最少的一组. 设\(n\)是满足 \[ a_{1}\sigma_{1}+\cdots+a_{n}\sigma_{n}=0,\ a_{i}\in\mathbb{K}	ext{不全为}0 \] 的最小的正整数. 则\(n\geq2\), \(a_{i}\)均不为 0. 因为\(\sigma_{1},\sigma_{2}\)不同, 故\(\exists z\in G\)使得\(\sigma_{1}(z)
eq\sigma_{2}(z)\). 对于任意\(x\in G\), 都有 \[ a_{1}\sigma_{1}(xz)+\cdots+a_{n}\sigma_{n}(xz)=0 \] 由于\(\sigma_{i}\)是同态, 则有 \[ a_{1}\sigma_{1}(z)\sigma_{1}+\cdots+a_{n}\sigma_{n}(z)\sigma_{n}=0 \] 两边同除\(\sigma_{1}\)并与第一个式子相减, 得 \[ \left(a_{2}\dfrac{\sigma_{2}(z)}{\sigma_{1}(z)}-a_{2}ight)\sigma_{2}+\cdots+\left(a_{n}\dfrac{\sigma_{n}(z)}{\sigma_{1}(z)}-a_{n}ight)\sigma_{n}=0 \] 其第一个系数就不为 0, 且比第一个式子少一个元素, 这与\(n\)的最小性矛盾. 因此, 任意一组两两不同的非零同态\(Gightarrow K^{*}\)在\(\mathbb{K}\)上线性无关. \(\square\) 问题 3 [Artin] 设\(\mathbb{E}\)为数域, \(G\)为\(\mathrm{Aut}\mathbb{E}\)的有限子群, 则\(\left|Gight|\geq\left[\mathbb{E}:\mathbb{F}ight]\). 证明: 设\(G=\{\sigma_{1}=\mathrm{id},\sigma_{2},\ldots,\sigma_{n}\}\). 要证\(\left[\mathbb{E}:\mathbb{F}ight]\leq\left|Gight|=n\), 只要证\(\mathbb{E}\)上任意\(n+1\)个元素在\(\mathbb{F}\)上线性相关. \( orall\alpha_{1},\alpha_{2},\ldots,\alpha_{n},\alpha_{n+1}\in\mathbb{E}\), 则\(\mathbb{E}\)上的线性方程组 \[  egin{pmatrix}\sigma_{1}(\alpha_{1}) &amp; \sigma_{1}(\alpha_{2}) &amp; \cdots &amp; \sigma_{1}(\alpha_{n+1})\ \sigma_{2}(\alpha_{1}) &amp; \sigma_{2}(\alpha_{2}) &amp; \cdots &amp; \sigma_{2}(\alpha_{n+1})\ \vdots &amp; \vdots &amp; &amp; \vdots\ \sigma_{n}(\alpha_{1}) &amp; \sigma_{n}(\alpha_{2}) &amp; \cdots &amp; \sigma_{1}(\alpha_{n+1}) \end{pmatrix}_{n	imes(n+1)} egin{pmatrix}x_{1}\ x_{2}\ \vdots\ x_{n+1} \end{pmatrix}=0 \] 必有非 0 解 (未知数的个数大于方程个数). 考虑其中包含非 0 元素最少的非零解\( egin{pmatrix}b_{1} &amp; b_{2} &amp; \cdots &amp; b_{m} &amp; 0 &amp; \cdots &amp; 0\end{pmatrix}\), 其中\(b_{i}
eq0,i=1,2,\ldots,m\). 不妨设\(b_{1}=1\), (否则考虑\( egin{pmatrix}1 &amp; \dfrac{b_{2}}{b_{1}} &amp; \cdots &amp; \dfrac{b_{m}}{b_{1}} &amp; 0 &amp; \cdots &amp; 0\end{pmatrix}\)). 方程组两边用\(\sigma_{i}\)作用, 由\(\sigma_{i}\)是同态, 可以得到\( egin{pmatrix}\sigma_{i}(b_{1}) &amp; \sigma_{i}(b_{2}) &amp; \cdots &amp; \sigma_{i}(b_{m}) &amp; 0 &amp; \cdots &amp; 0\end{pmatrix}\)是一组非零解, 其中\(\sigma_{i}(b_{1})=\sigma_{i}(1)=1\). 将两组解相减, 得 \[  egin{pmatrix}0 &amp; \sigma_{i}(b_{2})-b_{2} &amp; \cdots &amp; \sigma_{i}(b_{m})-b_{m} &amp; 0 &amp; \cdots &amp; 0\end{pmatrix} \] 也是一组非零解. 但这组解比\( egin{pmatrix}b_{1} &amp; b_{2} &amp; \cdots &amp; b_{m} &amp; 0 &amp; \cdots &amp; 0\end{pmatrix}\)含有更少的非零元, 因此它只能是零解, 即 \[ \sigma_{i}(b_{j})=b_{j},\  orall1\leq i\leq n,\ 1\leq j\leq m \] 由\(\mathbb{F}\)的定义知\(b_{j}\in\mathbb{F},\  orall1\leq j\leq m\). 所以 \[ 0=\sum_{j=1}^{n+1}\sigma_{1}(\alpha_{j})b_{j}=\sum_{j=1}^{n+1}\mathrm{id}(\alpha_{j})b_{j}=\sum_{j=1}^{n+1}b_{j}\alpha_{j} \] 这表明\(\alpha_{1},\ldots,\alpha_{n+1}\)在\(\mathbb{F}\)上线性相关. \(\square\)
